OL,5, Energy suppliers must give struggling  
OL,6, customers more chance to clear they    
OL,7, debts before forcibly switching them to
OL,8, a prepayment meter, Ofgem has said.    
OL,10,FNew rules outlined by the regulator    
OL,11,Fwill also see forced instalment banned 
OL,12,Fin the homes of customers over 85.     
OL,14,FThose with severe illnesses will also  
OL,15,Fbe exempt from forced switching when   
OL,16,Fbehind on payments.                    
OL,18,FIt comes after debt agents for British 
OL,19,FGas broke into some people's homes to  
OL,20,Ffit meters, sparking an outcry.        
